public class GenericJson
extends GenericData
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Generic JSON data that stores all unknown key name/value pairs.

Subclasses can declare fields for known data keys using the Key annotation. null unknown data key names are not allowed, but null data values are allowed.

2.2
